{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 5a depicts the structure of the CNN-LSTM applied in this research.",
    "In contrast to the CNN-LSTM model, the LSTM-CNN model first utilizes LSTM layers to associate the time series' data and output high-dimensional related hidden states.",
    "Subsequently, convolution layers are employed to extract the features of these time-dependent hidden states.",
    "This model has also been widely adopted in various applications (Xia et al., 2020).",
    "In this study, LSTM-CNN for soil moisture prediction consists of an LSTM layer and two convolution layers sequentially."
  ]
}